{"tid":1535260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠永遠係我哋嘅敵人","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:59:50.000Z","uid":153600,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5fe35a220046c0c8ce62749f73fbba50a647522","tid":1535260,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"呢班人唔係好似而家啲和理非<br />\n而家嘅和你非雖然做啲嘢係和平理性<br />\n但亦都會包容勇武，而且立場同勇武一樣<br />\n但呢班左膠大愛撚，只係想拎光環<br />\n會阻止勇武打狗同黑社會，仲會保護佢地<br />\n所以下次如果見到佢哋<br />\n就好似七月一號咁樣<br />\n拉撚走佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ad4797be4a12918f2aa643c586b65e66b539cd","tid":1535260,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e67c89390fb898c64ef6fd1962b09939a723ae63","tid":1535260,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:48:29.000Z","msg":"負皮，不推文，上一頁"},{"pid":"d394c79cd1baf60841bab4a601d16a793f1b299f","tid":1535260,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/im853ji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fim853ji.jpg&h=f0df50a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4v4zqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4v4zqY.jpg&h=d38a5073&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b9a60d42aec17b9efc2dbc97bd590b38ecb55a4","tid":1535260,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:49:15.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"21fa9c9a561e5a2208e26893a7a74f7cd7b35b19","tid":1535260,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"果班係鬼黎"},{"pid":"cf418bea5e50fe143d55ef8f401986bacab02432","tid":1535260,"uid":258115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:59:50.000Z","msg":"左膠最愛保護一個三番四次傷害手足嘅敵人<br />\n你保得佢一次壯大左佢個心，等佢知道原來打人實有左膠保，咁佢下次咪可以隨便出手，而且出手更重囉，最後咪更多手足因為呢個敵人受傷<br />\n你班左膠諗野點解咁表面？<br />\n<br />\n呢班敵人要嘅唔係保護，係教訓，等佢地知道邊個先出手打人都會有後果要受返。<br />\n以現時情況黎講，有邊次唔係班無腦藍絲先出手？有邊次有手足打人先？你班左膠最優先保嘅應該係手足，其次係唔好保敵人"}]}